data.title: WAGA TV FOX ATLANTA
data.meta_description:
15 reviews and 2 photos of WAGA TV FOX ATLANTA "Aside from the Today Show and Good Morning America, I actually enjoy watching Good Day Atlanta on Fox 5 TV.  The witty commentary of this diverse newscast is a true reflection of the direction Atlanta is headed in. Mark Hayes and Sunchita Vadlamani do a great job of bringing live and local news along with Brett Martin The Road Warrior and meteorologist Jeff Hill.

For local and national news mixed in with fun and entertainment tune into Good Day Atlanta from 6:00 a.m. to 9:00 a.m. Monday through Friday.  To find out more about the morning show and other news programming go to www.myfoxatlanta.com."
